sections.text: 48:12-61 to 48:12-66 of this title shall apply to any alterations, changes, relocations or openings ordered by the board of public utility commissioners prior to April fourteenth, one thousand nine hundred and thirty, if no part of the work under such order had been actually commenced on the ground on said date.
